            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Im a beginner in Zend Framework World ,I started with quickstart tutorial but I have a problem when I want to access a guestbook page an error is showed \n\nFatal error: Using $this when not in object context in D:\\qt\\quickstart\\application\\views\\scripts\\guestbook\\index.phtml on line 1\nThis is my index.phtml file:\n\n\/* this is an error line *\/\n<p><a href=\"<?php echo $this->url(\n    array(\n        'controller' => 'guestbook',\n        'action'     => 'sign'\n    ), \n    'default', \n    true) ?>\">Sign Our Guestbook<\/a><\/p>\n\nGuestbook Entries: <br \/>\n<dl>\n    <!-- Loop through the entries that were provided to us by the controller -->\n    <?php foreach ($this->entries as $entry): ?>\n    <dt><?php echo $this->escape($entry->email) ?><\/dt>\n    <dd><?php echo $this->escape($entry->comment) ?><\/dd>\n    <?php endforeach ?>\n<\/dl>\n"
